"title": "6672: grace, in human relationships",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6672: grace, in human relationships",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Undeserved favour or kindness, mercy, compassion and generosity are to be found in human relationships and are strongly encouraged in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Examples of grace in human relationships</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:10\">RUT 2:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:1-2Sam9:7\">2SA 9:1–9:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:2\">ACT 28:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:8-Gen33:11\">GEN 33:8–33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:12-Josh2:14\">JOS 2:12–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:6\">1SA 15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:18\">1SA 24:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:7\">1KI 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:25-Ps37:26\">PSA 37:25–37:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:8-Acts4:10\">ACT 4:8–4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:13\">1CO 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Grace in relationships encouraged</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27-Luke6:28\">LUK 6:27–6:28</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:44\">MAT 5:44</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:9\">PRO 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:7\">ROM 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:14\">PHM 1:14</a></p>\n<h3>Grace in relationships expressed as mercy and compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:7\">2CH 10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:9\">ZEC 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:13\">MAT 9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:32-Matt18:33\">MAT 18:32–18:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:36-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:36–10:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:3-Luke17:4\">LUK 17:3–17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1-Rom15:2\">ROM 15:1–15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:22\">JUD 1:22</a></p>\n<h3>Grace in relationships expressed as generosity and kindness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:10-Deut15:11\">DEU 15:10–15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:8\">1SA 25:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:5\">PSA 112:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:25-Prov11:27\">PRO 11:25–11:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:24\">1CO 10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:11-2Cor9:13\">2CO 9:11–9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:9-Gal6:10\">GAL 6:9–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:24\">2TI 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:16\">HEB 13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:7\">2PE 1:5–1:7</a></p>",
